E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20whole%20experience%20only%20reaffirmed%20my%20belief%20that%20if%20a%20couple%20is%20giving%20out%20plus-ones%2C%20all%20adults%20should%20get%20one%20%E2%80%94%20no%20exceptions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20certainly%20no%20vetting%20relationships%20for%20%26quot%3Bseriousness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20not%20be%20cheap%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20to%20ensure%20everyone%20feels%20welcome.%20If%20this%20isn't%20financially%20feasible%2C%20maybe%20couples%20should%20scale%20back%20their%20guest%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%20my%20friend's%20nuptials%2C%20I've%20come%20out%20as%20queer%2C%20and%20my%20stance%20on%20plus-ones%20has%20only%20become%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-time-tips-lgbtq-queer-dating-therapist-advice-relationship-expert-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQueer%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20necessarily%20follow%20the%20same%20milestones%20as%20heterosexual%20ones.%20What%20may%20be%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunserious%26quot%3B%20to%20outsiders%20could%20be%20your%20guest's%20most%20important%20person.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlash%20forward%20to%20two%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20different%20friend%20invited%20me%20to%20her%20wedding.%20I%20was%20single%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20after%20my%20previous%20experience%2C%20I%20wasn't%20expecting%20a%20plus-one.%20She%20offered%20one%20anyway%20and%20told%20me%20I%20could%20bring%20anyone%2C%20even%20just%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20going%20solo%20and%20having%20a%20great%20time.%20But%20the%20invitation%3F%20It%20made%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevery-single-adult-should-get-plus-ones-at-weddings-dates-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754227562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http