es%20nationwide%2C%20and%20KFC%20came%20in%2018th%20place%20among%20consumers.%20The%20legacy%20chain%20didn't%20break%20the%20top%205%20in%20any%20region%20across%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken%20chain's%20first%20phase%20of%20its%20comeback%20plan%20features%20a%20new%20addition%20%E2%80%94%20fried%20pickles%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20its%20expansive%20menu%2C%20which%20currently%20includes%20buckets%2C%20bowls%2C%20and%20combo%20meals%20of%20its%20fried%20chicken%2C%20as%20well%20as%20adjacent%20offerings%20like%20pot%20pies%2C%20waffles%2C%20tenders%2C%20nuggets%2C%20and%20sandwiches.%20While%20the%20chain%20bets%20on%20new%20menu%20innovations%2C%20it's%20also%20pushing%20a%20nostalgic%20vibe%2C%20with%20a%20resurgence%20of%20the%20chain's%20figurehead%2C%20the%20Colonel%2C%20in%20marketing%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatty-matheson-bio-chef-the-bear-actor-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMatty%20Matheson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Canadian%20celebrity%20chef%20known%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20acclaimed%20Hulu%20series%20%26quot%3BThe%20Bear%2C%26quot%3B%20will%20likewise%20star%20in%20a%20series%20of%20ads%20promoting%20the%20fried%20chicken%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Matheson%20is%20a%20burgeoning%20icon%20for%20Gen%20Z%20fans%2C%20Tan-Gillespie%20said%20his%20work%20as%20a%20spokesperson%20isn't%20about%20bridging%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmashburger-cofounder-tom-ryan-food-trends-generational-divide-research-development-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egenerational%20divide%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20KFC's%20consumers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20tend%20to%20think%20too%20much%20in%20sort%20of%20ages%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20a%20brand%20for%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Instead%2C%20Matheson%20%26quot%3Bwas%20just%20a%20perfect%20pairing%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20details%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20formally%20announced%2C%20Tan-Gillespie%20said%20to%20expect%20a%20series%20of%20forthcoming%20renovations%20to%20KFC's%20restaurants%2C%20which%20will%20give%20the%20chain%20a%20physical%20facelift%20to%20support%20its%20reinvigorated%20brand%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20not%20be%20exactly%20super%2C%20super%20sexy%2C%20but%20it's%20very%20simple%3A%20it's%20listening%20to%20what%20our%20customers%20want%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Tan-Gillespie%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e2235ee-baad-4741-ba93-53e008e8e779%5C%22%3EA%20promising%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0if%20it's%20played%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ER.J.%20Hottovy%2C%20head%20of%20analytical%20research%20at%20the%20location%20intelligence%20and%20foot%20traffic%20data%20software%20firm%2C%20Placer.ai%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20menu%20changes%2C%20free%20chicken%20promotion%2C%20and%20the%20new%20marketing%20campaign%20should%20help%20boost%20brand%20awareness%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20long%20road%20for%20KFC%20to%20restore%20its%20place%20in%20the%20chicken%20chain%20pecking%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20category%20remains%20fiercely%20competitive%2C%20and%20a%20true%20comeback%20will%20ultimately%20require%20more%20substantial%20enhancements%20to%20its%20menu%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20real%20estate%20strategies%2C%26quot%3B%20Hottovy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlacer.ai%20data%20recorded%20during%20the%20week%20of%20July%2014%20%E2%80%94%20which%20marked%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalue-meals-mcdonalds-wendys-taco-bell-fast-food-chain-strategy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecomeback%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20foot%20traffic%20at%20KFC%20locations%20nationwide%20down%200.1%25%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20While%20still%20a%20dip%2C%20that's%20a%20marked%20improvement%20from%20the%20week%20prior%2C%20when%20visits%20were%20do