0car%2C%20etc.%20But%20during%20my%20time%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20supply%20chains%20first-hand%20and%20how%20robotic%20it%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20growing%20her%20own%20food%20feels%20like%20a%20treat%20to%20the%20senses.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20express%20how%20freeing%20it%20feels.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdiem%20Farmstay%20boasts%20two%20cottages%20%E2%80%94%20a%20two-bedroom%20villa%20and%20a%20one-bedroom%20villa.%20The%20farmstay%20is%20powered%20by%20solar%20energy%20and%20has%20a%20brilliantly%20designed%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20system%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%2032%2C000%20litres%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Madhu.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20our%20day-to-day%20needs%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290271%2Fmumbai-rain-man-makes-rainwater-harvesting-system-using-low-cost-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharvest%20every%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20do%20not%20depend%20on%20the%20government%20at%20all.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20give%20the%20government%20approximately%201%2C200%20units%20every%20month.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7ZPNUwRLTW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC7ZPNUwRLTW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%