hop%20where%20we%20sell%20local%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20explains%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20include%20traditional%20handicrafts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20narrow%20down%20a%20date%20when%20you%20should%20plan%20a%20trip%2C%20we%20highly%20encourage%2019%20July.%20World%20Palace%20Day%20witnesses%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20only%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharashtra-heritage-stay-hotel-sustainable-tents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20royal%20residences%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20to%20do%20this%20%E2%80%93%20celebrate%20in%20line%20with%20the%20palaces%20of%20Europe.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20always%20a%20theme%20for%20the%20celebration.%20One%20year%20it%20was%20flora%20and%20fauna%3B%20the%20next%20year%20it%20was%20about%20mythology%20and%20last%20year%20they%20had%20an%20equestrian%20theme%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-9-1726574521.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20sees%20a%20host%20of%20events%2C%20pujas%2C%20celebrations%2C%20functions%20and%20events%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-9-1726574521.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-9-1726574521-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-9-1726574521-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0