r%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20sales%20and%20operations%2C%20Mohit%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20co-found%20the%20venture%2C%20focused%20on%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20and%20quality%20control.%20Together%2C%20they%20created%20a%20model%20they%20believed%20could%20transform%20rural%20livelihoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20path%20towards%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20we%20received%20an%20initial%20grant%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Their%20goal%20was%20to%20buy%20produce%20directly%20from%20farmers%20and%20offer%20them%20better%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20procured%20millets%20from%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20sold%20them%20to%20buyers%20in%20southern%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20in%20Hills%20operated%20in%20Uttarakhand%20by%20procuring%20millets%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%2C%20offering%20them%2010-15%25%20higher%20prices%20than%20the%20market%20rate%20as%20an%20incentive%20for%20their%20quality%20produce.%20The%20company%20provided%20primary%20processing%20services%2C%20including%20grading%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20cleaning%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20before%20selling%20them%20to%20bulk%20clients%20down%20south.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202020%20and%202021%2C%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20helped%20me%20earn%20approximately%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20could%20repay%20my%20loans%20and%20purchase%20essentials%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subdei%20(78)%2C%20from%20Luthiyag%20village%2C%20Rudraprayag%20district.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20traders%20would%20buy%20from%20me%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20me%20fairly.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20capable%20enough%20to%20run%20my%20business%2C%20trading%20pulses%20and%20millets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%